{"tha-ap184:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap184:0.2":"Kutajapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap184:0.3":"Bandhujivakattheraapadana ","tha-ap184:1.1":"“Siddhattho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap184:1.2":"sayambhu sabbhi vannito; ","tha-ap184:1.3":"Samadhim so samapanno, ","tha-ap184:1.4":"nisidi pabbatantare. ","tha-ap184:2.1":"Jatassare gavesanto, ","tha-ap184:2.2":"dakajam pupphamuttamam; ","tha-ap184:2.3":"Bandhujivakapupphani, ","tha-ap184:2.4":"addasam samanantaram. ","tha-ap184:3.1":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap184:3.2":"upagacchim mahamunim; ","tha-ap184:3.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap184:3.4":"siddhatthassabhiropayim. ","tha-ap184:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap184:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap184:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap184:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap184:5.1":"Ito catuddase kappe, ","tha-ap184:5.2":"eko asim janadhipo; ","tha-ap184:5.3":"Samuddakappo namena, ","tha-ap184:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap184:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap184:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap184:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap184:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bandhujivako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap184:8.1":"Bandhujivakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}